Me: Just me. I am making the decisions in my life.

Facilyn: Perfect. Then we treat you as the only decision-maker.

@dmkrs_include_more
title: Let's include the people
subtitle: that I live or decide with.
view-if: player = "one"
on-arrival: decision_makers = "Me and people I live or decide with"; player = "group"
go-to: 9_wum_physical_res
tags: decision_makers

Me: Let's include the people that I live or decide with.

Facilyn: Great. We’ll treat all of you together as the decision-makers in your whole under management.

# Group

@wum_dmkrs_group
title: Got it
view-if: player = "group"
tags: whole_u_mgmt

Me: Got it.

Facilyn: Let’s start with the decision-makers. In your group, who makes decisions? Who carries them out? And does anyone else have veto power?

Facilyn: Try to be inclusive rather than exclusive. 

